high_descs: Move the tomato off of the laddle, and place it in between two laddles. Turn to the left, and then the left again to find the microwave on the right side.
Open the microwave and take out the mug. Shut the microwave.
Carry the mug a few steps to the right, and find the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the mug inside and shut the door. Open the door again, take out the mug and shut the door.
Carry the mug and turn around. Turn to the left to go around the island to the brown shelf.
Place the mug on the next to bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Chill a mug and put it away on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Take the white cup out of the microwave and shut the door.
Go to the right and face the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out and shut the door again.
Turn around and go forward and then left and face the brown shelves.
Put the white cup on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup on a shelf.

open the door, put the mug on the top shelf, close door, wait, open door, pick up mug, close door
turn right, walk straight until facing stove, turn left, walk straight, stop at shelves
